data.title: Ken Olin
data.meta_description: Ken Olin is an actor and Producer of Alias, he's best known for his role in Thirtysomething (with his current wife Patricia Wettig), and the Series Brothers & Sisters (with Balthazar Getty, Ron Rifkin and Patricia Wettig), he played David McNeil in 1.10 Spirit, 1.14 The Coup and 1.15 Page 47.
data.text: Ken Olin is an actor and Producer of Alias, he's best known for his role in Thirtysomething (with his current wife Patricia Wettig), and the Series Brothers & Sisters (with Balthazar Getty, Ron Rifkin and Patricia Wettig), he played David McNeil in 1.10 Spirit, 1.14 The Coup and 1.15 Page 47.
